0href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchaos-erupts-after-thousands-palestinians-rush-to-grab-aid-gaza-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewar%20in%20Gaza%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInterest%20in%20AI's%20ability%20to%20anticipate%20humanity's%20most%20destructive%20urges%20comes%20as%20the%20world%20sees%20an%20alarming%20rise%20in%20global%20conflict.%20Last%20week%2C%20Israel%20launched%20strikes%20against%20Tehran%20under%20the%20pretense%20that%20the%20Ayatollah%20was%20inching%20closer%20to%20developing%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fimages-show-damage-iran-nuclear-facility-after-israel-strikes-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enuclear%20bomb%3C%2Fa%3E.%20A%20month%20ago%2C%20India%20and%20Pakistan%20came%20to%20the%20brink%20of%20war%20over%20the%20decadeslong%20dispute%20in%20Kashmir.%20The%20ongoing%20Gaza%20conflict%20has%20claimed%20more%20than%2050%2C000%20lives%2C%20and%20the%20war%20in%20Ukraine%20more%20than%20150%2C000%2C%20according%20to%20conservative%20estimates.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnadyr%20Horizon%20believes%20it%20can%20prevent%20war%20by%20using%20AI%20to%20create%20facsimiles%20of%20world%20leaders%20that%20live%20and%20interact%20in%20a%20simulation%20of%20the%20real%20world.%20Its%20software%2C%20North%20Star%2C%20is%20designed%20to%20predict%20how%20real-world%20decision-makers%20might%20react%20to%20a%20given%20situation%20or%20stimuli%20%E2%80%94%20like%20economic%20sanctions%20or%20a%20naval%20blockade%20%E2%80%94%20by%20observing%20their%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-agents-study-company-run-by-ai-disaster-replace-jobs-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAI%20counterparts%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Bell%20says%20these%20digital%20twins%20are%20so%20sophisticated%20that%20they%20can%20emulate%20how%20a%20leader%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fputin-business-allies-oppose-return-western-companies-russia-mcdonalds-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EVladimir%20Putin%3C%2Fa%3E%20might%20behave%20when%20he's%20sleep%20deprived%20versus%20having%20gotten%20a%20full%20night's%20rest.%20(Much%20of%20the%20formula%20behind%20these%20scores%20is%20Anadyr%20Horizon's%20secret%20sauce%2C%20but%20the%20Russian%20autocrat%20has%20boasted%20that%20he%20gets%20by%20on%20four%20hours%20of%20sleep.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20screen%2C%20North%20Star%20looks%20like%20the%201970s%20video%20game%20%26quot%3BThe%20Oregon%20Trail%2C%26quot%3B%20with%20reams%20of%20text%20chronicling%20events%20from%20the%20simulated%20world.%20Bell%20demonstrates%20by%20prompting%20it%20to%20show%20what%20would%20happen%20if%20the%20United%20States%20imposed%20a%20no-fly%20zone%20over%20Ukraine%20%E2%80%94%20a%20maneuver%20with%20a%20mixed%20history%20(e.g.%2C%20effective%20in%20preventing%20Saddam%20Hussein's%20regime%20from%20carpet-bombing%20southern%20Iraq%20in%201991%3B%20ineffective%20in%20preventing%20the%20Srebrenica%20massacre%20of%201995).%20North%20Star%20then%20runs%20thousands%20of%20simulations%2C%20each%20its%20own%20multiverse%20with%20slightly%20different%20variables%2C%20from%20whether%20a%20key%20decision-maker%20was%20late%20to%20work%20to%20the%20order%20in%20which%20a%20single%20conversation%20over%20military%20strategy%20might%20happen.%20It%20can%20model%20the%20outcomes%20of%20multiple%20different%20policies%2C%20and%20even%20offer%20advice%20on%20which%20leaders%20might%20be%20open%20to%20back%20channel%20negotiations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEventually%20the%20program%20spits%20out%20a%20result%3A%20Russia%20is%2060%25%20likely%20to%20escalate%20the%20conflict%20if%20a%20no-fly%20zone%20is%20imposed.%20It%20also%20provides%20a%20hypothetical%20SVR%20intelligence%20brief%20describing%20Russia's%20devastating%20escalation.%20%26quot%3BOver%20the%20past%2024%20hours%2C%20we%20have%20delivered%20high-precision%20strikes%20on%20enemy%20troop%20concentrations%20and%20military%20equipment%2C%20destroying%20ammunition%20depots%2C%20communication%20hubs%2C%20and%20infrastructure%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20reads.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20Bell%2C%20the%20origins%20of%20Anadyr%20Horizon%20were%20relatively%20low-tech.%20Back%20when%20he%20was%20a%20lecturer%20at%20Harvard%20%E2%80%94%20teaching%20courses%20in%20conflict%20de-escalation%20and%20post-Soviet%20geopolitics%20%E2%80%94%20he%20used%20funds%20from%20the%20university's%20startup%20incubator%2C%20the%20Scholar-Entrepreneur%20Initiative%2C%20to%20launch%20an%20organization%20that%20held%20a%20yearly%20war%20gaming%20event%20with%20high-profile%20representatives%20from%20the%20United%20States%20and%20the%20European%20Union.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMilitary%20and%20diplomatic%20leaders%20would%20join%20Bell%20in%20Cambridge%20and%20be%20assigned%20the%20role%20of%20a%20foreign%20dignitary%20%E2%80%94%20Gen.%20Zhang%20Youxia%2C%20the%20vice%20chairman%20of%20China's%20Central%20Military%20Commission%2C%20say.%20For%20three%20days%20of%20the%20event%2C%20they%20would%20become%20method%20actors%20going%20to%20painstaking%20lengths%20to%20re-create%20the%20lives%20of%20their%20assigned%20leaders%20as%20realistically%20as%20possible%2C%20wearing%20the%20same%20military%20fatigues%2C%20chauffeured%20in%20their%20preferred%20cars%2C%20and%20conferring%20in%20a%20replica%20of%20their%20situation%20room.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20like%20theater%2C%26quot%3B%20Bell%20tells%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBell%2C%20who'd%20been%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fyoutube-afghanistan-tiktok-adventure-taliban-tourism-influencers-ak47s-selfie-sticks-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etraveling%20to%20Afghanistan%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20a%20Ph.D.%20researcher%20over%20the%20past%20decade%2C%20drew%20from%20his%20experience%20studying%20breakdowns%20in%20negotiations%20during%20armed%20conflict.%20His%20goal%20was%20to%20have%20participants%20empathize%20with%20those%20they%20might%20otherwise%20see%20as%20their%20adversary.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222875%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Negotiation%20Task%20Force%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F685085ca85e81483682c32ea%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221619%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20senior%20military%20official%20who%20participated%20in%20a%20wargaming%20event%20at%20Harvard%20is%20greeted%20by%20another%20in%20a%20Chinese%20Communist%20Party%20uniform.%3Cp%3ENegotiation%20Task%20Force%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20one%20such%20event%20in%20December%202021%2C%20the%20Russian%20team%20invaded%20Ukraine%20using%20the%20exact%20multipronged%20military%20assault%20that%20Putin%20would%20use%2075%20days%20later.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETwo%20years%20later%2C%20he%20was%20introduced%20to%20Ferenc%20Dalnoki-Veress%2C%20a%20Nobel%20Prize-winning%20physicist%2C%20through%20Bill%20Potter%2C%20the%20founding%20director%20of%20the%20James%20Martin%20Center%20for%20Nonproliferation%20Studies%20at%20Middlebury%20College.%20At%20the%20time%2C%20Dalnoki-Veress%20was%20experimenting%20with%20prompting%20different%20AI%20agents%20to%20debate%20each%20other.%20%26quot%3BIt%20was%20something%20stupid%2C%26quot%3B%20Dalnoki-Veress%20says.%20%26quot%3BLike%20one%20agent%20has%20to%20prove%20to%20the%20other%20agent%20that%20cherry%20lollipops%20are%20better%20than%20lemon%20lollipops.%26quot%3B%20Dalnoki-Veress%20was%20impressed%20by%20the%20lengths%20that%20the%20robots%20would%20go%20to%20convince%20the%20others%20of%20their%20position.%20Sometimes%20they'd%20even%20lie%20to%20each%20other%20%E2%80%94%20if%20prompted%20to%20win%20at%20all%20costs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESoon%20he%20started%20experimenting%20with%20whether%20the%20agents%20would%20collaborate%2C%20negotiate%2C%20or%20even%20write%20treaties%20with%20one%20another.%20%26quot%3BIt%20occurred%20to%20me%20how%20human%20it%20was%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Dalnoki-Veress.%20Last%20fall%2C%20the%20trio%20of%20academics%20founded%20Anadyr%20with%20the%20belief%20they%20could%20imbue%20these%20bots%20with%20the%20personalities%20of%20world%20leaders%20and%20realistically%20emulate%20their%20interactions.%20Instead%20of%20organizing%20one%20war%20game%20a%20year%2C%20they%20could%20game%20out%20hundreds%20of%20thousands%20of%20scenarios%20over%20the%20course%20of%20one%20night%20and%20get%20%26quot%3Bprobabilistic%20estimates%20of%20where%20conflicts%20are%20really%20going%20to%20happen%2C%26quot%3B%20Bell%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20hopes%20North%20Star's%20predictive%20capabilities%20will%20help%20diplomats%20and%20politicians%20make%20better%20decisions%20about%20how%20to%20negotiate%20during%20times%20of%20conflict%20and%20even%20prevent%20wars.%20Anadyr%20is%20a%20reference%20to%20the%20code%20name%20the%20USSR%20used%20for%20its%20deployment%20of%20ballistic%20missiles%20and%20warfighters%20to%20the%20western%20coasts%20of%20Cuba%20in%20October%201962.%20If%20President%20John%20F.%20Kennedy%20had%20a%20tool%20like%20North%20Star%20to%20preempt%20the%20Cuban%20Missile%20Crisis%2C%20Bell%20posits%2C%20instead%20of%20having%2013%20days%20to%20respond%2C%20he%20might%20have%20had%20six%20months.%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20reclaiming%20this%20name%20to%20say%2C%20'OK%2C%20the%20next%20Operation%20Anadyr%2C%20we%20will%20detect%20early%2C'%26quot%3B%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20doing%20so%2C%20the%20company%20and%20its%20venture%20capital%20backers%20believe%20it%20can%20make%20billions.%20By%20some%20estimates%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.economicsandpeace.org%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FGPI-2024-web.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eviolent%20conflict%20cost%20the%20global%20economy%20%2419%20trillion%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202023%20alone.%20And%20one%20study%20conducted%20by%20the%20International%20Monetary%20Fund%20suggests%20every%20dollar%20spent%20on%20conflict%20prevention%20can%20yield%20a%20return%20as%20high%20as%20%24103%20in%20countries%20that%20have%20recently%20experienced%20violent%20conflict.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPeace%20tech%20is%20going%20after%20a%20huge%20market%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Brian%20Abrams%2C%20a%20founder%20of%20B%20Ventures%2C%20an%20investor%20in%20Anadyr.%20%26quot%3BIf%20you%20look%20at%20climate%20tech%2C%20a%20decade%20ago%2C%20the%20space%20was%20very%20small.%20It%20wasn't%20even%20called%20climate%20tech%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20adds.%20%26quot%3BNow%2C%20climate%20tech%20sees%20about%20%2450%20billion%20in%20investment%20annually.%26quot%3B%20He%20says%20peace%20tech%20can%20replicate%20the%20growth%20seen%20in%20the%20climate%20tech%20industry.%20Anadyr's%20early%20clients%20aren't%20confined%20to%20just%20state%20agencies%3B%20the%20company%20is%20also%20selling%20its%20software%20to%20corporate%20risk%20managers%20who%20want%20to%20understand%20how%20social%20unrest%20might%20affect%20their%20investments%20and%20assets%20in%20different%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnadyr%20has%20also%20raised%20funds%20from%20Commonweal%20Ventures%2C%20an%20early%20investor%20in%20the%20defense%20contractor%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpalantir-stock-price-pltr-alex-karp-ai-government-retail-traders-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPalantir%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20AIN%20Ventures%2C%20a%20veteran-led%20firm%20that%20invests%20in%20technologies%20that%20can%20be%20useful%20in%20both%20the%20military%20and%20in%20the%20private%20sector.%20Bell%20says%20they've%20already%20been%20able%20to%20close%20a%20seven-figure%20pre-seed%20round%2C%20though%20he%20didn't%20disclose%20the%20exact%20figures.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20a%20company%20dedicated%20to%20preventing%20war%20had%20chosen%20a%20defense%20expo%20to%20unveil%20its%20product%20wasn't%20lost%20on%20Bell.%20But%20the%20lines%20between%20peace%20and%20war%20technology%20are%20blurrier%20than%20they%20may%20seem.%20The%20defense%20contractor%20Rhombus%20Power%2C%20a%20sponsor%20of%20the%20expo%2C%20has%20its%20own%20AI%20conflict%20prediction%20software%20that%20it%20says%20made%20accurate%20predictions%20of%20Russia's%20invasion%20of%20Ukraine.%20%26quot%3BWe%20look%20at%20peace%20tech%20as%20the%20flip%20side%20of%20the%20same%20coin%2C%26quot%3B%20Abrams%20says.%20According%20to%20Abrams%2C%20the%20size%20of%20the%20defense%20industry%20shows%20that%20there%20is%20a%20market%20for%20technology%20seeking%20to%20prevent%20war.%20%26quot%3BThe%20difference%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20says%2C%20between%20peace%20tech%20and%20war%20tech%20is%20%26quot%3Ba%20different%20approach%20to%20the%20same%20problem.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20the%20audience%20at%20Bell's%20demo%20had%20its%20fair%20share%20of%20defense%20tech%20funders%20in%20attendance.%20When%20one%20of%20the%20venture%20capitalists%20in%20the%20crowd%20asks%20whether%20he's%20considered%20the%20technology's%20military%20applications%2C%20he%20tells%20them%20that's%20a%20line%20too%20far%20for%20Anadyr%20Horizon%2C%20at%20present.%20%26quot%3BFor%20now%20we're%20definitely%20focused%20on%20the%20strategic%20level%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20says.%20%26quot%3BBecause%20we're%20trying%20to%20stop%20war.%26quot%3B%20A%20savvy%20salesman%2C%20he%20adds%20%E2%80%94%20%26quot%3Bwe're%20still%20early%20enough%20to%20see%20where%20the%20market%20will%20pull%20us.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EOver%20lunch%2C%20I%20ask%20the%20founders%20if%20they%20believe%20something%20is%20lost%20in%20automating%20the%20war%20games%20Bell%20conducted%20at%20Harvard.%20%26quot%3BWhat%20you're%20losing%2C%26quot%3B%20Bell%20concedes%2C%20%26quot%3Bis%20the%20extremely%20personal%20and%20emotional%20experience%20of%20an%20American%20admiral%20who%20is%20put%20into%20the%20shoes%20of%20his%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchina-as-many-icbms-as-us-russia-by-2030-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EChinese%20counterpart%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20for%20the%20first%20time%20is%20looking%20at%20American%20warships%20coming%20to%20his%20coast.%26quot%3B%20But%20you%20can%20only%20run%20such%20a%20realistic%20simulation%20with%20real%20people%20a%20few%20times%20a%20year.%20%26quot%3BThe%20capabilities%20of%20AI%20are%20exponential%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20says.%20%26quot%3BThe%20impact%20is%20on%20a%20much%20greater%20scale.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20other%20challenges%20with%20using%20artificial%20intelligence%20for%20something%20as%20high-stakes%20as%20preventing%20the%20next%20world%20war.%20Researchers%20have%20long%20warned%20that%20AI%20models%20may%20hold%20biases%20hidden%20in%20the%20data%20from%20which%20they%20were%20trained.%20%26quot%3BPeople%20say%20history%20is%20written%20by%20the%20victor%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fex-google-researcher-openai-board-diversity-timnit-gebru-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETimnit%20Gebru%2C%20an%20AI%20researcher%3C%2Fa%3E%20who%20fled%20Eritrea%20in%201998%2C%20during%20the%20country's%20war%20with%20Ethiopia.%20An%20AI%20system%20trained%20on%20open-source%20information%20on%20the%20internet%2C%20she%20says%2C%20will%20inherently%20represent%20the%20biases%20of%20the%20most%20online%20groups%20%E2%80%94%20which%20tend%20to%20be%20Western%20or%20European.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20notion%20that%20you're%20going%20to%20use%20a%20lot%20of%20data%20on%20the%20internet%20and%20therefore%20represent%20some%20sort%20of%20unbiased%20truth%20is%20already%20fraught%2C%26quot%3B%20Gebru%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20founders%20are%20unwilling%20to%20reveal%20the%20actual%20data%20their%20digital%20world%20leaders%20are%20trained%20on%2C%20but%20they%20do%20offer%20that%20Anadyr%20Horizon%20uses%20%26quot%3Bproprietary%20datasets%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchatgpt-openai-ai-dictionary-help-understand-nvidia-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eopen-source%20intelligence%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20coded%20behavioral%20inputs%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20and%20that%20they%20go%20to%20great%20lengths%20to%20use%20books%20and%20data%20from%20outside%20the%20English-speaking%20world%20to%20account%20for%20differing%20world%20views.%20The%20leaders%20they%20emulate%2C%20Bell%20says%2C%20use%20as%20many%20as%20150%20datapoints.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBiases%20in%20these%20new%20AI%20systems%20are%20especially%20hard%20to%20interrogate%20not%20only%20because%20of%20this%20lack%20of%20transparency%20around%20the%20data%20used%20by%20the%20systems%2C%20but%20also%20because%20of%20how%20the%20chatbots%20interpret%20that%20information.%20In%20the%20case%20of%20generative%20AI%2C%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fworld-model-ai-explained-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eintelligence%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20is%20a%20misnomer%20%E2%80%94%20%26quot%3Bthey're%20essentially%20spitting%20out%20a%20likely%20sequence%20of%20words%2C%26quot%3B%20Gebru%20says.%20This%20is%20why%20bots%20are%20so%20prone%20to%20confidently%20expressing%20falsehoods.%20They%20don't%20actually%20know%20what%20they're%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20also%20hard%20to%20trace%20why%20they%20make%20certain%20decisions.%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnvidia-brands-using-ai-boost-marketing-delta-unilever-mars-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENeural%20networks%3C%2Fa%3E%20aren't%20explainable%2C%26quot%3B%20Gebru%20says.%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20like%20a%20regression%20model%20where%20you%20can%20go%20back%20and%20see%20how%20and%20why%20it%20made%20predictions%20in%20certain%20ways.%26quot%3B%20One%20study%20into%20the%20use%20of%20large%20language%20models%20for%20diplomatic%20decision-making%2C%20conducted%20last%20year%20by%20researchers%20at%20Stanford%2C%20found%20that%20AI%20models%20tended%20to%20be%20warmongers.%20%26quot%3BIt%20appears%20LLM-based%20agents%20tended%20to%20equate%20increased%20military%20spending%20and%20deterrent