0and%20Bangladesh%2C%20notes%20the%20inherent%20unpredictability%20of%20war%2C%20with%20contingencies%20and%20factors%20that%20can't%20always%20be%20accounted%20for.%20%26quot%3BIf%20you%20look%20at%20what's%20going%20to%20happen%20with%20Israel%20taking%20action%20against%20Iran's%20nuclear%20program%2C%20you%20can%20do%20all%20kinds%20of%20scenarios%20on%20how%20that's%20going%20to%20play%20out.%20I'm%20sure%20there's%20somebody%20who's%20going%20to%20make%20a%20prediction%2C%20which%20after%20the%20fact%20they'll%20be%20able%20to%20say%20they%20were%20right.%20But%20what%20about%20the%20multiples%20that%20got%20it%20totally%20wrong%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20never%20certainty%20in%20these%20kinds%20of%20decision-making%20situations%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Bell.%20%26quot%3BIn%20some%20senses%2C%20we%20can't%20predict%20the%20future.%20But%20we%20can%20assign%20probabilities.%20Then%20it's%20up%20to%20the%20user%20to%20decide%20what%20to%20do.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20meantime%2C%20the%20company%20has%20more%20pressing%20problems.%20Like%20many%20startups%20building%20on%20top%20of%20generative%20AI%20models%2C%20the%20costs%20to%20run%20North%20Star%20are%20huge.%20%26quot%3BI%20don't%20want%20to%20give%20you%20a%20figure%2C%20but%20if%20you%20knew%2C%20you'd%20drop%20your%20fork.%20It's%20extremely%20expensive%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20says.%20On%20top%20of%20that%2C%20contracting%20with%20the%20government%20and%20receiving%20the%20necessary%20clearances%20can%20be%20its%20own%20set%20of%20bureaucratic%20red%20tape%20and%20expenses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20this%2C%20there%20seems%20to%20be%20no%20shortage%20of%20interest%20in%20their%20technology.%20As%20I%20leave%20Bell%20and%20Dalnoki-Veress%2C%20they%20rush%20off%20to%20another%20meeting%3A%20Eric%20Schmidt's%20office%20wanted%20a%20private%20demonstration.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fauthor%2Ftekendra-parmar%5C%22%20target%3D