y%20he%20gifted%20me%20a%20Swarovski%20pendant%20in%20the%20shape%20of%20a%20lock%20with%20a%20small%20gold%20key%20attached%20to%20it%20with%20a%20note%20which%20read%2C%20%E2%80%9CMay%20you%20find%20the%20key%20to%20unlock%20all%20your%20hopes%20and%20dreams%2C%20and%20you%20may%20not%20know%20it%20but%20the%20lock%20is%20within%20you%2C%20and%20the%20key%20is%20also%20within%20you%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20writes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Fhemant-karkare-2-1750083223.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Whether%20it%20was%20birthday%20surprises%20or%20guiding%20his%20children%20with%20their%20career-related%20dilemmas%2C%20Hemant%20Karkare%20is%20remembered%20by%20his%20children%20for%20being%20a%20pillar%20in%20their%20lives%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Fhemant-karkare-2-1750083223.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Fhemant-karkare-2-1750083223-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Fhemant-karkare-2-1750083223-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Fhemant-karkare-2-1750083223-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Fhemant-karkare-2-1750083223-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-450314%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EWhether%20it%20was%20birthday%20surprises%20or%20guiding%20his%20children%20with%20their%20career-related%20dilemmas%2C%20Hemant%20Karkare%20is%20remembered%20by%20his%20children%20for%20being%20a%20pillar%20in%20their%20lives%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20siblings%20credit%20their%20dad%20for%20giving%20them%20the%20agency%20to%20dream.%20%E2%80%9CEven%20when%20it%20came%20to%20our%20careers%2C%20or%20when%20someone%20would%20ask%20him%20for%20professional%20advice%2C%20he%20would%20say%2C%20%E2%80%98The%20scope%20lies%20in%20the%20person%20and%20not%20in%20the%20field.%E2%80%99%20He%E2%80%99d%20worked%20as%20an%20engineer%20years%20before%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F424663%2Fvisually-impaired-manu-garg-secures-air-91-in-upsce-cse-with-political-science-optional-paper%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eappearing%20for%20the%20UPSC%20and%20getting%20selected%3C%2Fa%3E.%20He%20always%20maintained%20that%20giving%20your%20best%20to%20the%20field%20you%20choose%20is%20more%20important%20than%20focusing%20too%20much%20on%20the%20scope%20of%20the%20field%20you%20choose.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20lessons%20live%20on%20in%20his%20favourite%20dialogue%20%E2%80%94%20%E2%80%9Clife%20is%20full%20of%20pluses%20and%20minuses%E2%80%9D.%20His%20genius%20lay%20in%20his%20ability%20to%20bring%20an%20emotional%20depth%20to%20every%20conversation.%20Jui%20shares%20an%20anecdote%2C%20%E2%80%9CDuring%20my%20engineering%20days%2C%20I%20did%20not%20score%20well%2C%20this%20one%20time.%20When%20I%20told%20Papa%2C%20he%20showed%20me%20his%20engineering%20report%20card%20and%20pointed%20out%20that%20he%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20among%20the%20top%20three.%20He%20told%20me%20that%20marks%20were%20not%20important%2C%20but%20one%E2%80%99s%20approach%20is.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKarkare%E2%80%99s%20precision%20was%20razor-sharp%20on%20the%20field%20and%20off%20it%2C%20too.%20%E2%80%9CPapa%20maintained%20well-manicured%20lawns%2C%20he%20had%20an%20eye%20for%20detail%2C%20and%20loved%20gardening.%20He%20encouraged%20my%20siblings%20and%20me%20to%20plant%20saplings%2C%E2%80%9D%20Jui%20shares.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20in%20Chandrapur%2C%20he%20started%20dabbling%20in%20