Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20a%20bit%20of%20a%20setback%2C%20but%20not%20one%20that%20discouraged%20him.%20Instead%2C%20it%20forced%20Gaurav%20to%20think%20more%20carefully%20about%20what%20kind%20of%20space%20BDC%20really%20needed%20%E2%80%94%20somewhere%20sheltered%2C%20accessible%2C%20and%20open%20to%20everyone.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMore%20importantly%2C%20he%20wanted%20it%20to%20feel%20welcoming%20for%20anyone%20who%20walked%20in%2C%20no%20matter%20who%20they%20were.%20%E2%80%9CWherever%20there%20is%20public%2C%20stories%20start%20brewing%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says%2C%20explaining%20why%2C%20from%20the%20very%20beginning%2C%20BDC%20was%20designed%20to%20be%20community-friendly%2C%20family-friendly%2C%20and%20earth-friendly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFinding%20the%20right%20space%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Cubbon%20Park%20hiccup%20made%20one%20thing%20clear%3A%20if%20this%20was%20going%20to%20work%2C%20they%20needed%20a%20proper%20space.%20One%20that%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20get%20disrupted%2C%20one%20that%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20depend%20on%20the%20weather%2C%20and%20most%20importantly%2C%20one%20where%20people%20would%20feel%20comfortable%20showing%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%E2%80%99s%20when%20Bangalore%20Creative%20Circus%20came%20into%20the%20picture%20%E2%80%94%20an%20old%20warehouse%20that%20had%20been%20transformed%20into%20a%20creative%20space%20for%20artists%2C%20musicians%2C%20and%20performers.%20It%20ticked%20every%20box.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%204%20June%202023%2C%20BDC%20held%20its%20first%20official%20session%20there.%20Gaurav%20went%20in%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F391614%2Fparai-beat-history-caste-barriers-revival%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewith%20his%20own%20drum%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20brought%20along%20two%20extras%2C%20just%20in%20case.%20%E2%80%9CI%20made%20them%20sit%20and%20play%20with%20me.%20And%20I%20said%2C%20I%20want%20to%20do%20this%